text: Sproughton (pronounced Spror-ton) is a village and civil parish in Babergh, Suffolk, England, just to the west of Ipswich. In 2016, there were 764 people living in Sproughton. == References == == Other websites == * Sproughton Church * Photographs at SuffolkCam * Sproughton Tennis Club Category:Civil parishes in Suffolk Category:Villages in Suffolk
